Description: AtoM Heratio - Modern GLAM/DAM Platform
 AtoM Heratio transforms Access to Memory (AtoM) 2.10 into a modern
 Laravel-based GLAM/DAM platform with Bootstrap 5 theme, 79 plugins,
 AI automation, digital preservation, and multi-jurisdiction compliance.
 .
 Three installation modes:
   complete     - AtoM 2.10 + Heratio framework + all plugins (recommended)
   atom-only    - Vanilla AtoM 2.10 (no Heratio)
   heratio-only - Layer Heratio onto existing AtoM >= 2.8
 .
 Features include:
   - Bootstrap 5 responsive theme
   - GLAM sector plugins (Library, Museum, Gallery, DAM)
   - AI automation (NER, translation, summarization, OCR)
   - Digital preservation (PREMIS, fixity, PRONOM)
   - Multi-jurisdiction compliance (POPIA, GDPR, CCPA, NARSSA)
   - OAIS-aligned batch ingest with 6-step wizard
   - Web-based configuration wizard
